const explainer = `
If you want to use a font without installing it on your device, follow these simple steps:

1. **Go to the Website:** Open your browser and visit [www.dafont.style](https://www.dafont.style).
2. **Find Your Font:** Browse the website and select the font you like.
3. **Open the Font Page:** Click on the font to open its page.
4. **Preview Your Text:** In the preview section, type your custom text. Adjust size, style, and other settings.
5. **Download the Image:** Once your text looks perfect, download the image. You can use it anywhere—on social media, presentations, or graphics—without installing the font.

This is why **Dafont.style** is becoming so popular—it lets you use fonts easily without the hassle of installation.
`;
